{"tid":1082773,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你身邊既圈子到底係生活富裕定係貧窮既佔多數？","createTime":"2019-03-29T07:28:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-29T11:13:26.000Z","uid":27415,"like":26,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"714d8143e023bd89bc0561fd1d2b083f3ebeab6f","tid":1082773,"uid":27415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T07:28:41.000Z","msg":"出街見D人都好捨得消費，好似完全無考慮錢既問題，初中學生都全民拎iPhone，咩貴袋。<br />\n<br />\n大把人住公屋都每年去旅行，講緊每半年去日本係基本，偶爾去歐洲遊歷幾個國家既都有。<br />\n<br />\n更加唔洗提全民都咁喜歡買名牌，男既就靚錶，女就手袋。<br />\n<br />\n除左樓，香港人係有咩買唔起？<br />\niPhone咁貴，連公屋仔都隨隨便便就負擔到年年換電話啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要拍拖又俾曬D洗費，女友生日要book五星酒店海景房過夜慶祝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">計我話香港人rich到仆街啊！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />- 身邊多數朋友係過富裕生活，物質豐富 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />-仆街啦 樓主我識個D同我一樣咩都要慳，過得無尊嚴<br />\n<br />\n（注意：你住公屋都可以物質好豐富，宜家係講緊有無錢可以洗，唔係你原生家庭個個「階層」所屬）"},{"pid":"85c488c6adcc8c3fd6d134971897529048bcadcb","tid":1082773,"uid":27415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T07:29:24.000Z","msg":"不服來辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cb1664cc903afa37a0f2831c29b2fab0e95701b","tid":1082773,"uid":27415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T07:30:04.000Z","msg":"plan緊去旅行既你，唔洗扮窮啦喂"},{"pid":"72d8a1857d545ad26dd1d69e223eca21abdf7d42","tid":1082773,"uid":27415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T07:32:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6480af3834e87c6dc3ba41292ba0d73dcc8f06e6","tid":1082773,"uid":27415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T07:33:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"