e2d72a0ec54604fe0","tid":1082773,"uid":137096,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T07:49:28.000Z","msg":"可以同你講越有錢嘅會越慳 唔會浪費啲錢喺啲無謂嘢到<br />\n其實中學生個個拎住杯黑糖屎水唔代表依家呢一代有錢咗<br />\n反而反映緊而家啲人喜歡show off（social media效應）想俾人覺得自己有錢 咪拎杯30$ 嘅屎水打下卡咁<br />\n咁你上social media自然咪睇到個撚個都發咗達咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T07:51:25.000Z","msg":"但係都有錢洗，你先會咁做？<br />\n<br />\n如果你真係窮，你無左$30，第二日就少一餐飯錢。<br />\n<br />\n如果未工作既學生妹都唔洗擔心聽日無得開飯，咪即係富裕左囉。<br />\n<br />\n唔通10-20年前D人讀書可以讀到咁多閒錢買奶茶，咖啡飲咩，有個麥當勞都慶祝啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e055ea3121e6bc128f8d4a25484a100632b473b","tid":1082773,"uid":27415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T07:56:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a507410b3239c967f5be947836ccbd529f875aad","tid":1082773,"uid":27415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T08:13:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ecc0d6ced5f1a625687a425f330263ad0357299","tid":1082773,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T09:51:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=m6pWEzkbnDE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dm6pWEzkbnDE&d=88BycQanWGa6BXzVat85HcRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=27b3f33b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=m6pWEzkbnDE</a>"},{"pid":"e10b9ab463decb510b2025889d8e3754550e6400","tid":1082773,"uid":126118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T09:56:17.000Z","msg":"月入7萬，有樓有現金，買嘢食嘢口唔會睇價錢，一年至少一次歐遊3星期，去亞洲國家無計次數，當郊游，都係耐去長洲同入元朗少少，夠唔夠chill?"},{"pid":"cbb8eb4d97a789b96718421e7a777f6e1979d0f8","tid":1082773,"uid":128761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2fc7c0e9f492f4aacae04342853f260cb089149","tid":1082773,"uid":55189,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T07:37:05